    "content": {
      "scenario": "Minimal Pair 🎯: /ɪ/ vs /iː/ (EN)",
      "text": "<b>Identify the phoneme:</b><br><a href='https://forvo.com/word/ship/#en' target='_blank'>🔊 /ɪ/</a> vs <a href='https://forvo.com/word/sheep/#en' target='_blank'>🔊 /iː/</a><br><br>First phoneme IPA: {{c1::short, relaxed, mid-high front vowel}}",
      "explanation": "<b>Phoneme A:</b> /ɪ/ — IPA: <code>short, relaxed, mid-high front vowel</code><br><b>Phoneme B:</b> /iː/ — IPA: <code>long, tense, high front vowel</code><br><br><b>Articulatory Tip (ES):</b> Para /ɪ/, relaja la boca y la lengua completamente. Es corta. Para /iː/, sonríe exageradamente y tensa los lados de la lengua. Es más larga.<br><br><table border='1' cellpadding='4'><thead><tr><th>Word (/ɪ/)</th><th>IPA</th><th>Word (/iː/)</th><th>IPA</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/ship/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>ship</b></td><td><code>/ʃɪp/</code></td><td><b>sheep</b></td><td><code>/ʃiːp/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/ship/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>bit</b></td><td><code>/bɪt/</code></td><td><b>beat</b></td><td><code>/biːt/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/ship/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>sit</b></td><td><code>/sɪt/</code></td><td><b>seat</b></td><td><code>/siːt/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/ship/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>fit</b></td><td><code>/fɪt/</code></td><td><b>feet</b></td><td><code>/fiːt/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/ship/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>fill</b></td><td><code>/fɪl/</code></td><td><b>feel</b></td><td><code>/fiːl/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/ship/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>grin</b></td><td><code>/ɡrɪn/</code></td><td><b>green</b></td><td><code>/ɡriːn/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/ship/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>slip</b></td><td><code>/slɪp/</code></td><td><b>sleep</b></td><td><code>/sliːp/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/ship/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>hit</b></td><td><code>/hɪt/</code></td><td><b>heat</b></td><td><code>/hiːt/</code></td></tr></tbody></table>",
      "spanish": "Para /ɪ/, relaja la boca y la lengua completamente. Es corta. Para /iː/, sonríe exageradamente y tensa los lados de la lengua. Es más larga.",
