      "scenario": "Minimal Pair 🎯: /æ/ vs /ɛ/ (EN)",
      "text": "<b>Identify the phoneme:</b><br><a href='https://forvo.com/word/bad/#en' target='_blank'>🔊 /æ/</a> vs <a href='https://forvo.com/word/bed/#en' target='_blank'>🔊 /ɛ/</a><br><br>First phoneme IPA: {{c1::short, near-open front unrounded vowel}}",
      "explanation": "<b>Phoneme A:</b> /æ/ — IPA: <code>short, near-open front unrounded vowel</code><br><b>Phoneme B:</b> /ɛ/ — IPA: <code>short, open-mid front unrounded vowel</code><br><br><b>Articulatory Tip (ES):</b> Para /æ/, abre la boca de manera lateral (sonrisa exagerada) y empuja la lengua hacia adelante y abajo. Para /ɛ/, abre la boca de manera neutra (parecido a la 'e' de cama).<br><br><table border='1' cellpadding='4'><thead><tr><th>Word (/æ/)</th><th>IPA</th><th>Word (/ɛ/)</th><th>IPA</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/bad/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>bad</b></td><td><code>/bæd/</code></td><td><b>bed</b></td><td><code>/bɛd/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/bad/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>man</b></td><td><code>/mæn/</code></td><td><b>men</b></td><td><code>/mɛn/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/bad/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>sad</b></td><td><code>/sæd/</code></td><td><b>said</b></td><td><code>/sɛd/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/bad/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>pan</b></td><td><code>/pæn/</code></td><td><b>pen</b></td><td><code>/pɛn/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/bad/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>tan</b></td><td><code>/tæn/</code></td><td><b>ten</b></td><td><code>/tɛn/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/bad/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>bag</b></td><td><code>/bæg/</code></td><td><b>beg</b></td><td><code>/bɛg/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/bad/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>dad</b></td><td><code>/dæd/</code></td><td><b>dead</b></td><td><code>/dɛd/</code></td></tr><tr><td><a href='https://forvo.com/word/bad/#en' target='_blank'>🔊</a> <b>land</b></td><td><code>/lænd/</code></td><td><b>lend</b></td><td><code>/lɛnd/</code></td></tr></tbody></table>",
      "spanish": "Para /æ/, abre la boca de manera lateral (sonrisa exagerada) y empuja la lengua hacia adelante y abajo. Para /ɛ/, abre la boca de manera neutra (parecido a la 'e' de cama).",
